messages.content: Hey Carina, I hope you're well! My name's Isa, and I'm a woman living in London. I'm running a creative auction for my Gazan friend's urgent fundraiser, and I was wondering if you'd like to contribute a donation? I've already collabed with Ayesha Sureya who's also in No Borders with you, and it was a success. If you'd like to work together please do let me know! Thanks so much
